ai-patthana14.36:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma ladies that are difficult for the living, etc.,
ai-patthana14.36:1.1_0: Uttara is not supreme cause or reason.
ai-patthana14.36:2.1_2: There is no supreme cause or condition for the supreme.
ai-patthana14.36:3.1_0: In the supreme state arises dependent on the supreme, not the supreme Teaching.
